# File Structure Adherence
- Strict hierarchy: /backend, /backend/service, /frontend
- Components: src/components/TreeConnections.tsx, PersonaEditor.tsx, SynthGen.tsx, ChatEvals.tsx, DictExport.tsx.
- Utils: src/utils/versionControl.js (simple-git), syntheticData.js (PyTorch/PennyLane).
- Never create flat files or deviate—e.g., no dumping in root; always modular (one feature per file).
- On edits: Validate against this structure; refactor if off-spec.
- Example: New persona versioning → src/features/personas/versionManager.ts + test in tests/features/.